<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM4.1">
<l>teḷḷi yārpalar kaitoḻun tēvaṉār</l>
<l>vaḷḷal māliruñ cōlai maṇāḷaṉār</l>
<l>paḷḷi koḷḷu miṭattaṭi koṭṭiṭak</l>
<l>koḷḷu mākilnī kūṭiṭu kūṭalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O circle ! [You] be joined if</l>
<l rend="indent">the Lord whom many enlightened people worship with joined hands,</l>
<l rend="indent">the Generous One, the Bridegroom from Māliruñcōlai</l>
<l>accepts [me] to pat [His] feet at the place where [He] sleeps.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
